Akulearn Solar System Maintenance Checklist

Weekly:
- Clean solar panels
- Inspect wiring and connectors
- Check fuses and breakers

Monthly:
- Test battery voltage and capacity
- Inspect enclosure seals and ventilation

Yearly:
- Replace batteries if capacity < 80%
- Inspect and clean all hardware

Field Notes:
- Record all maintenance actions and findings
- Report any faults or anomalies immediately
